Text:
This is more like a compilation of short movies than one feature film so it is a little disjointed... And I thin it is all in Portuguese. That said, there are some INCREDIBLY hot scenes in this that make it worth the download. There's MT, TM, TMT, MTF, MTM, and about every combination imaginable.

It looks like these were ripped from VHS. There's some flicker at the top in some clips and the audio is tinny in some clips.

A: 9
V: 9
M: 10

If you're into Trannys this is definitely worth the download
